data.name: infoText.Text
data.value:
Taz Wanted trainer and patcher v1.1
Trainer usage: launch game and use keys to activate cheats. Patcher usage: while the game is not running select necessary patches and click "Patch!". Apply pathes after configuring options and controls in native game launcher and make sure that path to Taz.exe in Windows registry is correct. Backup of exe file will be created automatically in game directory. Click "Restore all" to restore all settings to original, or "Restore .exe" to restore only Taz.exe file from backup.
